data.name: RetailerInvoice_NotificationEmail_Body
data.value:
Dear Blinkay Merchant,

All the studies indicate that regulated parking helps a greater number of vehicles to rotate, and therefore more customers can access the highly-attended shopping areas. If your business is located in a regulated area, you are lucky that it means you probably have a large influx of citizens and potential customers. However, it is still true that local commerce has a big handicap regarding large stores, a pending task to be solved: the payment of the regulated area.

We trust that this new service that we put at your disposal will help you get more new customers and strengthen the current ones. Do not doubt that the parking bonus is a great incentive for a customer to opt for their trade and not another area. The more you reward, the more customers you will have!

Attached to this email we provide you with a PDF where you can obtain the bonus coupons for your customers. Each of these coupons has a unique code engraved with the amount that will be rewarded, and are for single use. Do not hesitate to contact our support team for more questions through www.blinkay.app.

Thank you for trusting Blinkay,

Cheers!
